ParLocationValuation is a BusinessTask
    owned by ic

    Patterns
        implements ManualTransaction
        implements StaticJava
            is report for SupplyManagementProcessor, Buyer, InventoryManager, ParLevelSpecialist, PurchasingManager, WarehouseClerk, ApplicationAdministrator, SupplyManagementViewer, Inventory
                category is "Valuation"
                report name is "ParLocationValuation"
				Description
					Calculate the value of all items in a cart/par location.
                    Report shows the par quantity and the sum of extended costs of the par quantity for all items in the cart/par location or report group.
            Reports
                ParLocationValuationReport

    Parameters
        Company                 is an InventoryCompany
        ReportGrp               is an InventoryReportGroup
        Location                is an InventoryLocation
        UpdatePar               is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                No  value is "N"
                    default label is "No"
                Yes value is "Y"
                    default label is "Yes, Pars with items"
                All	value is "A"
                	default label is "Yes, All Pars"    
        DisplayOption			is AlphaUpper size 1
			States
				Location 		value is "L"
				ReportGroup 	value is "R"
				

	Parameter Rules
		Company
			required
		UpdatePar
			initial value is "N"
			default to "N"

    Actions
        ParLocationValuation is a Set Action
            allow unlimited concurrency
